reviewText: The "monkey show" is popular at our house and this is just another dvd in the series. All are good and we have several.
Title: Curious George: Sweet Dreams

reviewText: This is one of our favorite PBS shows and has captured my 4 year old Grandson's attention since before he was 2 - so it was a slam dunk purchase.
Title: Curious George: Sweet Dreams

reviewText: I'm not sure exactly why our 4 year old loves Curious George but I'm betting it has something to do with a kinship she feels with him.  They are both terminally curious about life and find amusement in every thing.
Title: Curious George: Sweet Dreams

reviewText: I purchased this for our daughter as a "welcome to our new home" present when we moved...  It was a good distraction from the new and unfamiliar surroundings...  She loves George and has several other shows in the series so it was a nice comfort to have an old friend while boxes were unpacked...  It has quickly become a favorite...just like the others :)
Title: Curious George: Sweet Dreams

reviewText: Keeps the child interested, great way to educate a child. You have the cartoon, and also the story applied in real life.
